    "created_at": "2015-11-16T17:27:08Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-16T17:27:33Z",
    "body": "Atom is seeing a raft of new font issues reported in the last week or two:\n\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom/issues/9596\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom/issues/9454\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom/issues/9226\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom/issues/9161\n\nI think this is a Chrome 45 bug, hopefully Chrome 47 drops soon so we can move to it\n"
  },
  {
    "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/electron/electron/issues/comments/157199165",
