    "created_at": "2015-11-16T23:05:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-16T23:05:46Z",
    "body": "Also, since this seems to affect a pretty big portion of Atom's user base, do you think downgrading to the previous version of Electron in Atom could be an option? It would be a sort of a bummer but we're not really sure about how long it's going to take to fix that problem in the Chromium codebase.\n\nThoughts?\n\n/cc: @nathansobo @benogle \n"
  },
