    "body": "Thanks, @zcbenz. I'll make sure to open a PR on Atom that upgrades Electron to the latest version, so that we can test if this fix solves the issue on Linux. After having a second :eyes: on the Windows reports for blurry text on Atom, I feel like it _could_ be related to another issue (subpixel font scaling + tiling), although at this point I am not sure what's triggering this behavior on the Slack app.\n"
