    "updated_at": "2016-08-10T15:52:40Z",
    "body": "It's worth pointing out that Chromium M53 will [enable \"use zoom for dsf\" by default](https://codereview.chromium.org/2173243002/patch/1/10001), meaning that this change should eventually trickle down to Electron and fix a lot of the blurriness discussed here.\n"
